				PRINTFORML 「You're either brave, or have a screw loose～」
				PRINTFORMDW Flandre smirks playfully as you square up.
				PRINTFORML 「Still, if you want to be the best――」
				PRINTFORMDW She crosses her arms, and begins exerting an immense pressure.
				PRINTFORML 「――you gotta learn from the best!」
				PRINTFORMDW Here she comes!
				PRINTFORMDW ...
				PRINTFORML 「Hahaha! Missed again!」
				PRINTFORMDW Throughout the session, she effortlessly outmaneuvers you, her movements swift and teasing.
				PRINTFORML 「Nana-na-na-naa-na～」
				PRINTFORMDW After dodging another of your attempts, she effortlessly knocks you to the ground.
				PRINTFORML 「You're fun, %CALLNAME:MASTER%!」
				PRINTFORMDW Flandre remarks in a light-hearted manner.
				PRINTFORML 「Here.」
				PRINTFORMDW She extends a hand to help you up with a grin.
				PRINTFORMW 「Ready for round two?」
		ENDSELECT
	ELSEIF ABL:[[フラン]]:戦闘能力 == ABL:MASTER:戦闘能力
		PRINTFORML 「Oho～ You wanna play with me?」
		PRINTFORMDW Flandre grins, accepting the challenge with a sparkle of excitement in her eyes.
		PRINTFORMDW You ready yourself.
		PRINTFORMDW ...
		PRINTFORMDW As the training progresses, it's clear you're evenly matched.
		PRINTFORMDW Flandre's moves are quick and cunning, but you keep up pace for pace.
		PRINTFORMDW After a particularly skillful exchange, she steps back, laughing.
		PRINTFORML 「You're full of surprises, %CALLNAME:MASTER%!」
		PRINTFORML 「I didn't expect you to be able to keep up with me like this!」
		PRINTFORMDW She says, her tone brimming with playfulness.
		PRINTFORMDW Circling back into stance, she winks.
		PRINTFORML 「This is getting interesting! Ready for another round?」
		PRINTFORMDW She teases, clearly enjoying herself.
	ELSE
		PRINTFORML 「Hahaha! This is so fun, %CALLNAME:MASTER%!」
		PRINTFORMDW One of the four Flandres says as your attack connects with another one.
		PRINTFORML 「Keep it up!」
		PRINTFORMDW The remaining two clones fade back into the original. The original then takes out a spell card.
		PRINTFORML 「Taboo "Lævateinn"!」
		PRINTFORMDW She brandishes a giant sword of flame, clearly too big for even her to use effectively.
		PRINTFORMDW You manage to keep your distance and dodge near the tips of the swings.
		PRINTFORMDW You're about to counter attack when suddenly――
		PRINTFORML 「Ack!」
