					PRINTFORMDW She leans into the gesture, a contented smile gracing her lips.
					PRINTFORML 「I feel like a princess～❤」
					PRINTFORMDW Her gaze meets yours, full of love and appreciation.

			ENDSELECT
		ENDIF
	ENDIF

